<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.4">
<l>uraṅkaḷāli yaṉṟamaṉ ṉarmāḷap pāratat torutē raivarkkāyc ceṉṟu</l>
<l>viraṅkiyūrnta varkkiṉ ṉaruḷcey yumem pirāṉai vampārpuṉal kāviri</l>
<l>yaraṅkamāḷi yeṉṉāḷi viṇṇāḷi yāḻicūḻi laṅkai malaṅkac ceṉṟu</l>
<l>caraṅkaḷāṇṭa taṇṭāma raikkaṇṇa ṉukkaṉṟi yeṉmaṉan tāḻntunil lātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without our lord who gave the Five his sweet grace,</l>
<l rend="indent">going for their sake in the Bhārata [War],</l>
<l>Showing [them] compassion, driving a chariot,</l>
<l rend="indent">so that kings who advanced with troops died,</l>
<l>The ruler of Araṅkam with fragrance-filled waters of the Kāviri,</l>
<l rend="indent">ruler over me, ruler of heaven,</l>
<l>The one with cool lotus eyes who used arrows, going to harass Lankā</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by the sea, my mind will not stay focused.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
